{"tid":93494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚吉野家打邊爐","createTime":"2017-01-24T13:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T13:25:51.000Z","uid":19946,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"697254e1c47afa32a4103b1b417254f80b31b9c2","tid":93494,"uid":19946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"肚餓想打邊爐又無人陪就自己毒撚食<br />\n對面坐咗對情侣一直閃住我對眼<br />\n個女嘅一直係到雞仔聲嗲個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住係到又抱又錫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬啊我食野啊係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望住睇到我好嬲但又唔夠膽講咩<br />\n身邊嘅人又一直以恥笑嘅眼光望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個人打邊爐真係咁好笑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人有過相同經歷求安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:絲"},{"pid":"afb3bc79bf746ee7028ed1305697d38334412b74","tid":93494,"uid":48573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:01:35.000Z","msg":"肥絲？"},{"pid":"dd3e0d9c32aedc14ddfdd314679beefb56d968d9","tid":93494,"uid":19946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥絲？</blockquote><br />\n唔肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002223339e9f09a4c7030d1a390a69ca50056808","tid":93494,"uid":7615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:04:06.000Z","msg":"我都試過 好彩有帶耳塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102e275b3d2709830ee938e18b2dd31f187f6cd1","tid":93494,"uid":38315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:04:19.000Z","msg":"低質釣狗公"},{"pid":"37d249b1c3b72d89efe080af385fe06b128a264f","tid":93494,"uid":19946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T13:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過 好彩有帶耳塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" cl